== What Does Not Work ==
Flashing is possible, but there are problems:
* booting off SD is necessary as system and userdata partitions are too small for the current image
* attempting to boot using <nowiki>pmbootstrap flasher boot</nowiki> fails after printing the cmdline to the screen.

